race.comment: LE TROY (2) improved sharply winning as favourite over 1400m at Leinster eight days ago. Put 5L on them after being in contention on the corner. Has his share of talent and hard to beat in this suitable race. IMA WILD GIRL (1) fought on for third last start over 1400m at Leinster, beaten 3L in stronger. Placed prior as well and her best figures measure up. FAST JOHN (3) improved sharply with a 1L win over 1400m at Leonora two weeks ago, leading them up. Finds a tough easier and has claims again. URBAN WARRIOR (4) proved too strong two runs ago at Leonora but couldn't follow that up last time out over 1600m at Leinster. Comes back to a sprint but keeps the handy 3kg claim and should be around the mark.
